## Description {#details}

A base class holding non-template-dependant functionality of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/acceltable">AccelTable</a> class.

Clients should not use this class directly but rather instantiate <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/acceltable">AccelTable</a> with a type derived from <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/acceltabledata">AccelTableData</a>.

Definition at line 135 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/acceltable-h">AccelTable.h</a>.
